Anki is a program which makes remembering things easy. Because it is a lot more efficient than traditional study methods, you can either greatly decrease your time spent studying, or greatly increase the amount you learn.
http://ankisrs.net/

This project allows to fill the Anki learning deck with the translated words from English to Russian with transcription and pronunciation. The data is requesting from google dictionary, parsing, downloading media files and preparing single txt file with all translated words ready to be imported into the Anki deck. Media files are downloading in the audio directory and then should be places in the deck's media folder.

Files descriptions:
  input.txt - put your text here
  output.txt - contains words and translations, need to be imported to Anki deck
  words.txt - contains found words
  missed.txt - words failed to be translated

For output.txt generation just prepare input.txt and then run main.php without any parameters.